ce:section.ce:para:
Serotransferrin, N-lobe and Serotransferrin C-lobe are the two principal chains in HTF structure [37]. HDOCK server was used for the simulation of (Hb-HTF) RES as a ternary system. Also, the molecular docking between the energy-minimized Hb and HTF was carried out through HDOCK (
                              https://hdock.phys.hust.edu.cn/
                           ), a hybrid algorithm of template-base modeling, and ab initio free docking. The top-ranked protein–protein complex was chosen from the top ten postures predicted by HDOCK based on the energy scores, which were contrasted by evaluation criteria such as the docking score, RMSD (Å), and receptor interface residue (polar) [38].
